## 12. 发布系统

### 12.1 网站发布

文章生成后，通过 API 将文章状态从 `draft` 更新为 `published`。Next.js 通过 ISR（Incremental Static Regeneration）自动更新页面。

```typescript
// 发布流程
async function publishToWebsite(articleId: string): Promise<void> {
  // 1. 更新文章状态
  await articleStore.updateStatus(articleId, 'published');
  
  // 2. 触发 Next.js 按需重新验证
  await fetch(`${WEBSITE_URL}/api/revalidate`, {
    method: 'POST',
    body: JSON.stringify({ articleId }),
  });
}
```

### 12.2 社交媒体发布 (X/Twitter)

#### 发布内容生成

```typescript
interface SocialPostContent {
  text: string;       // 推文正文
  url: string;        // 文章链接
}

function generateTweetContent(article: Article): SocialPostContent {
  const sourceMix = article.sourceIds.length;
  return {
    text: `🧪 New from AI Journal\n\n"${article.title}"\n\nA ${article.style} blend of ${sourceMix} unrelated topics.\n\nRead more:`,
    url: `${WEBSITE_URL}/article/${article.id}`,
  };
}
```

#### X API 集成

```typescript
async function postToTwitter(content: SocialPostContent): Promise<string> {
  const response = await fetch('https://api.twitter.com/2/tweets', {
    method: 'POST',
    headers: {
      'Authorization': `Bearer ${TWITTER_BEARER_TOKEN}`,
      'Content-Type': 'application/json',
    },
    body: JSON.stringify({
      text: `${content.text}\n${content.url}`,
    }),
  });

  const data = await response.json();
  if (data.errors) {
    throw new Error(`Twitter API error: ${JSON.stringify(data.errors)}`);
  }
  return data.data.id;
}
```

