## 13. 调度与自动化

### 13.1 每日执行流程

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["⏰ Cron Trigger\n(Daily 00:00 UTC)"] --> B["Step 1: Crawl All Sources"]
    B --> B2["Step 2: Dedup Filter\n(URL + Title Similarity)"]
    B2 --> C["Step 3: Store in Metadata Layer"]
    C --> D["Step 4: Run AI Gatekeeper\n(Stage 1)"]
    D --> E["Step 5: Content Reveal"]
    E --> E2["Step 6: Run AI Curator\n(Stage 1.5)"]
    E2 --> F["Step 7: Run Story Generator\n(Stage 2)"]
    F --> G["Step 8: Store Article\n(status: draft)"]
    G --> H{"Auto-publish?"}
    H -->|Yes| I["Step 9a: Publish to Website"]
    H -->|No| J["Step 9b: Queue for Review"]
    I --> K["Step 10: Post to Social Media"]
    K --> L["Step 11: Health Check\n(Source Monitor)"]
    J --> L
    L --> M["Done ✅"]

    style A fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#2563eb,color:#fff
    style B2 fill:#ec4899,stroke:#db2777,color:#fff
    style D fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#d97706,color:#000
    style E2 fill:#06b6d4,stroke:#0891b2,color:#fff
    style F fill:#8b5cf6,stroke:#7c3aed,color:#fff
    style L fill:#6366f1,stroke:#4f46e5,color:#fff
    style M fill:#22c55e,stroke:#16a34a,color:#fff
```

### 13.2 调度配置

```yaml
# cron-schedule.yml
schedules:
  # 每小时抓取高频源
  crawl-frequent:
    cron: "0 * * * *"         # 每小时
    sources: [bbc, techcrunch, hackernews]

  # 每6小时抓取低频源
  crawl-infrequent:
    cron: "0 */6 * * *"       # 每6小时
    sources: [arxiv, nature]

  # 每天生成一篇文章
  generate-article:
    cron: "0 8 * * *"         # 每天 UTC 08:00 (确保有当天的新鲜素材)
    maxSources: 30
    articleStyle: random       # 随机选择风格

  # 每天发布到社交媒体
  social-post:
    cron: "0 12 * * *"        # 每天 UTC 12:00 (阅读高峰时段)
```

### 13.3 实现方式

| 方案 | MVP 推荐 | 生产推荐 |
|------|----------|----------|
| **Node-cron** | ✅ 简单直接 | — |
| **Vercel Cron** | ✅ 零运维 | ✅ |
| **GitHub Actions** | ✅ 免费 | — |
| BullMQ + Redis | — | ✅ 高可靠 |

